snippet.title: FROGUE - Announcement Trailer | Nintendo Switch, PS4, PS5, Xbox One and Xbox Series S|X
snippet.description:
FROGUE is a stylish turn-based action platformer with roguelike, bullet-hell, and time manipulation elements. It's coming soon to consoles.
